    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/b3f034cc475a83b30139cdf7a7566bd7.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" width=512 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/b3f034cc475a83b30139cdf7a7566bd7.webm?t=1765821813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/b3f034cc475a83b30139cdf7a7566bd7.mp4?t=1765821813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Welcome to the bloodletting...</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Days before high school's end, one of your friends decided to bring to light the existence of an abandoned film studio underneath the school. From within the dusty sepulcher everything went black. Then reality struck as you came to. The students have vanished. All of your friends are gone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stammering creatures now wander the halls. You choke on your breath; the air here is disgusting. The walls here are moving. Pulsating. You remember a voice, made clear to your unconscious mind: &quot;<strong>END THE CYCLE.</strong>&quot; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Newfound power lies before you. Unravel the mystery. Escape this hell.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/21cd9d4b1767531b7531f121e73e5e29.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" width=512 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/21cd9d4b1767531b7531f121e73e5e29.webm?t=1765821813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/21cd9d4b1767531b7531f121e73e5e29.mp4?t=1765821813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/05c2dbcdbf87407e3dd4181746a31d28.apng?t=1765821813\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/05c2dbcdbf87407e3dd4181746a31d28.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=125 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/8562575aaa8a65c342765b3f4ff2a120.apng?t=1765821813\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/8562575aaa8a65c342765b3f4ff2a120.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=125 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/d35b24043fe735a458530aa372fc2f2e.apng?t=1765821813\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/d35b24043fe735a458530aa372fc2f2e.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=125 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/f710f2598b62636ac9e0ac31e0e7291d.apng?t=1765821813\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194790/extras/f710f2598b62636ac9e0ac31e0e7291d.poster.avif?t=1765821813\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=125 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Features</u></i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore dingy surrealist environments... </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fixed camera horror with light survival elements, use the fixed camera to defeat enemies and solve puzzles... </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form a pact with a God to ensure your safety...  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
